00:07:46.530 --> 00:07:48.190
the planet at the same
rate that the planet spins

00:07:48.190 --> 00:07:49.830
on its axis, which I
agree is not something

00:07:49.830 --> 00:07:51.720
that should happen if the
moon is also gradually getting

00:07:51.720 --> 00:07:52.220
closer.

00:07:52.220 --> 00:07:54.632
It's a major inaccuracy in
the game, and as I said,

00:07:54.632 --> 00:07:55.840
I don't have all the answers.

